We need to minimize the time to complete totalTrips, this gives an intutition that binary search can be applied. The problem will be having a predicate function with respect to time taken like this

F F F F ... F F T T T ... T T

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
First of all find the range in which the time can vary. So, the total time required will have a minimum value equal to the minimum value in the array and we can take a safe maximum value equal to the sum of the elements of the array multiply by the totalTrips.

